  "description": "G02 Research Graph. Verifies approved claims and finds current literature for a lecture refresh, then freezes a UserApprovedResearchBundle. SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for the node order — g02_flow.py and the orchestrator skill must agree with this manifest. Authoritative design: docs/02_Architektura_agentow_i_skilli.md. Reviews are runs of ONE physical agent (g02-a10-output-reviewer) with a per-node review_profile; each producer run receives at most one review. APPROVED continues, BLOCKED stops, and REVISE permits one deterministically finalized producer correction without re-review. The two user gates are orchestrator steps, not agents. g02_flow.py keeps an injectable no-op wiring harness, while reviewed_flow.py runs the implemented fast frontier through reviewed A09, pauses at Human Research Gate, and finalizes the bundle only after resume approval. Discovery and A07 remain serial; concurrency requires explicit dependency and scheduler support.",
